President Bill Clinton and a young former intern filter into the
public domain, Clinton allies are slowly unwinding a fragile string
of explanations to protect him against charges of perjury and
obstruction of justice. US-CLINTON-INVESTIGATION. Has moved. By Ron
Fournier.
	   GOMA, Congo _ Rebels battling to topple President Laurent Kabila
accuse Angola of entering the fray in Congo's escalating war, which
already includes forces from Zimbabwe and threatens to engulf other
African states. CONGO-REBELS. RECAP expected by 0300 GMT. By Hrvoje
