cities along the Yangtze River, and soldiers in the northeast fight
to stop a breached levee hard by China's largest oil field.
CHINA-FLOODS. Has moved. By Charles Hutzler.
	   OMAGH, Northern Ireland _ Silence falls upon this bomb-shattered
town and across Ireland in memory of 28 people slain by IRA
dissidents, as another band of anti-British outlaws responds to the
atrocity by announcing their own cease-fire. NORTHERN IRELAND. Has
moved. By Shawn Pogatchnik. AP Photos XMA101,XOGH105,107,LON104.
	   Also moved:
	   _NIRELAND-INLA ATTACKS. Irish National Liberation Army's 23-year
record of bloodshed.
	   SANTO DOMINGO, Dominican Republic _ Caribbean nations sign a
