Has moved. By Dan Perry. AP Photo SDO101,104.
	   LUCKNOW, India _ Rescue workers run for cover when boulders
hurtle down on a remote Himalayan village where 202 people were
already feared killed in an earlier landslide. INDIA-LANDSLIDES.
Has moved. By Jaideep Mazumdar.
	   BONN, Germany _ Opposition candidate Gerhard Schroeder kicks off
